Construct a PHP program to read a file using file operation.

CODE:
<?php
$filename = "sample.txt";  // File to read

// Check if file exists
if (file_exists($filename)) {
    $file = fopen($filename, "r");  // Open file in read mode

    echo "<h3>File Content:</h3>";
    // Read file line by line until end
    while (!feof($file)) {
        echo fgets($file) . "<br>";
    }

    fclose($file);  // Close file
} else {
    echo "File not found!";
}
?>

OUTPUT:
File not found!
